'''佛波醇-12-十四烷酰-13-乙酸酯''' {{lang|en|(12-''O''-Tetradecanoylphorbol-13-acetate,TPA)}}是一種具有潛在[[促癌|促癌作用]]的[[佛波酯|佛波酯]]，在生物醫學研究中常用作[[蛋白激酶C|蛋白激酶C]]{{lang|en|(Protein kinase C,PKC)}}的激活劑。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Castagna et al | title = "Direct activation of calcium-activated, phospholipid-dependent protein kinase by tumor-promoting phorbol esters"| year = 1982 | journal = [[Journal_of_Biological_Chemistry|Journal of Biological Chemistry]] | volume =  257 | issue = 13 | pages = 7847–7851}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Blumberg | title = "Protein kinase C as the receptor for the phorbol ester tumor promoters: sixth Rhoads memorial award lecture" | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_cancer-research_1988-03_48/page/1 | year = 1988 | journal = [[Cancer_Research_(journal)|Cancer Research]] | volume =  48 | pages = 1–8}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Niedel et al | year = 1983 | journal = [[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences]] | volume = 80 | pages = 36–40 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.80.1.36 | title = Phorbol Diester Receptor Copurifies with Protein Kinase C}}</ref> TPA對PKC的生物學活性源於它的擬[[甘油二酯|甘油二酯]]({{lang|en|Diglyceride}})樣作用——後者是一種經典蛋白激酶C的天然活化劑。 

在自由基生物學中，不包含[[羥基自由基|羥基自由基]]、[[過氧化氫|過氧化氫]]、[[過氧亞硝酸鹽|過氧亞硝酸鹽]]在內的[[超氧化物|超氧化物]]被認定系TPA而非[[离子霉素|离子霉素]]（{{lang|en|Ionomycin}}）在小鼠[[巨噬細胞|巨噬細胞]]中產生的活性氧衍生物，因此TPA已成為誘生內源性超氧化物的常規用劑。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Swindle | title =  "A Comparison of Reactive Oxygen Species Generation by Rat Peritoneal Macrophages and Mast Cells Using the Highly Sensitive Real-Time Chemiluminescent Probe Pholasin: Inhibition of Antigen-Induced Mast Cell Degranulation by Macrophage-Derived Hydrogen Peroxide" | year = 2002 | journal = [[The_journal_of_Immunology|The journal of Immunology]] | volume =  169 | pages = 5866-5873}}.</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Huang | title =  "Megakaryocytic Differentiation of K562 Cells Induced by PMA Reduced the Activity of Respiratory Chain Complex IV"| year = 2014 | journal = [[PLOS_ONE_(journal)|PLOS ONE (journal)]] | volume =  9 | pages = e96246}}.</ref> 

在[[細胞遺傳學|細胞遺傳學]]試驗中，TPA被視為[[B細胞淋巴瘤|B細胞淋巴瘤]]細胞的[[丝裂原|有丝分裂原]]({{lang|en|Mitogen}})，可刺激B細胞的分裂以便於對特定細胞的染色體進行觀察，從而幫助診斷諸如[[慢性淋巴细胞白血病|慢性淋巴细胞白血病]]的[[血液癌症|血液癌症]]。<ref>''The AGT cytogenetics laboratory manual''. 3rd ed. Barch, Margaret J., Knutsen, Turid., Spurbeck, Jack L., eds. 1997. Lippincott-Raven.</ref>

TPA與離子黴素的聯合製劑已被廣泛用於刺激T細胞的活化、增殖並產生[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]，亦可用作[[细胞内染色|细胞内染色]]的助劑。<ref name="urlFlow Cytometry Intracellular Staining Guide">{{cite web | url = http://www.ebioscience.com/resources/best-protocols/flow-cytometry/flow-cytometry-intracellular-staining-quick-guide.htm | title = Flow Cytometry Intracellular Staining Guide | author =  | date =  | work =  | publisher = eBioscience, Inc | accessdate = 2011-09-25 | archive-date = 2017-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170121081102/http://www.ebioscience.com/resources/best-protocols/flow-cytometry/flow-cytometry-intracellular-staining-quick-guide.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

